Vaccination_Event_TypeObject.description: Display information used to describe an instance of an object. This 'optional' information is for outbound descriptive purposes only and is not processed on inbound Workday Web Services requests.

Vaccination_Event_TypeObject.description: Contains a unique identifier for an instance of an object.

Vaccination_Event_Type_Data.description: Contains a unique identifier for an instance of an object.
The type of vaccination event workers can select when entering their vaccination. Example: First Dose.
If true, the vaccination event type is inactivated. You might have downstream impacts if there's existing vaccination data.
